                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0.35cm;line-height: 115%;text-align: left;background: transparent;""><strong>BOTIQUIN :</strong></p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;""><strong>Normas :</strong></p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Colocado en lugar seguro y seco, sin humedad.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Mantenerlo limpio siempre.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">No guardar medica");
                WriteLiteral(@"mentos dentro ni otros productos que no sean de curas.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Sólo el material necesario para una primera cura.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Que no esté al alcance de los niños.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Revisarlo periódicamente y cambiar aquellos productos caducados.</p>


                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;""><strong>Material :</strong></p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Guantes .</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">1 o 2 triángulos.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;l");
                WriteLiteral(@"ine-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Vendas 2 o 3 medidas.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Gasas esterilizadas.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Gasas (Linitul).</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Suero fisiológico o liquido para lavado de heridas.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Desinfectante.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Esparadrapo (papel, ropa y plástico).</p>

