                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Agua Oxigenada.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Hielo sintético.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Tijeras (para ropa y esterilizadas para piel).</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Pinzas esterilizadas.</p>

                    <p style=""margin-bottom: 0cm;line-height: 100%;text-align: left;background: transparent;"">Termómetro.</p>

